==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sniggle
<hw>Snig"gle</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To catch, as an eel, by
sniggling; hence, to hook; to insnare.</def> <rj><au>Beau. &
Fl.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

